snippet.title: Project Demigod - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Project Demigod is the ultimate superhero simulator. Stage physics-driven comic book battles in a limitless sandbox. Toss cars into ninjas with super strength, swing through cityscapes or master tactile melee weapons.

Create your own superhero by mixing powers together for unique combinations. In Project Demigod, you decide what type of hero to be. Who will you become?

Early Access & App Lab is available now, full version arrives in 2024!

Purchase Project Demigod on App Lab for Meta Quest 2, 3 and Pro: https://www.meta.com/en-gb/experiences/5288522424560925/

Purchase Project Demigod on Steam Early Access for PC VR: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1646580/Project_Demigod/
